01:03:24.460 --> 01:03:28.570 align:middle line:10%
It can be any color you wish
or combination of colors.

01:03:28.570 --> 01:03:33.530 align:middle line:10%
And this beam of light is so
strong and powerful that it

01:03:33.530 --> 01:03:38.960 align:middle line:10%
creates a big aura-- a big
ball of aura around you

01:03:38.960 --> 01:03:40.415 align:middle line:10%
to protect you with light.

01:03:40.415 --> 01:03:43.920 align:middle line:90%


01:03:43.920 --> 01:03:46.800 align:middle line:10%
And this beam of
light shoots out

01:03:46.800 --> 01:03:51.670 align:middle line:10%
through the soles of your
feet and into the Earth

01:03:51.670 --> 01:03:56.150 align:middle line:10%
to ground you in this physical
so that you shall always

01:03:56.150 --> 01:03:59.680 align:middle line:10%
feel grounded here
while you are here.

01:03:59.680 --> 01:04:01.910 align:middle line:10%
And as it shoots
out into the earth,

01:04:01.910 --> 01:04:09.720 align:middle line:10%
it branches out so that it has
a nice, strong foothold here,

01:04:09.720 --> 01:04:13.380 align:middle line:10%
because for now, you
are meant to be here,

01:04:13.380 --> 01:04:16.900 align:middle line:10%
because you have a purpose.

01:04:16.900 --> 01:04:17.935 align:middle line:10%
You have a purpose.

01:04:17.935 --> 01:04:20.760 align:middle line:10%


01:04:20.760 --> 01:04:22.835 align:middle line:10%
And your purpose
is becoming clear.

01:04:22.835 --> 01:04:26.096 align:middle line:90%


01:04:26.096 --> 01:04:28.280 align:middle line:10%
your purpose is clarifying.

01:04:28.280 --> 01:04:36.830 align:middle line:90%


01:04:36.830 --> 01:04:40.780 align:middle line:10%
And slowly, I want you to start
feeling your physical body

01:04:40.780 --> 01:04:41.580 align:middle line:10%
again.

01:04:41.580 --> 01:04:44.260 align:middle line:10%


01:04:44.260 --> 01:04:49.890 align:middle line:10%
Your body is feeling
powerful and strong

01:04:49.890 --> 01:04:52.590 align:middle line:10%
and with intention and purpose.

01:04:52.590 --> 01:04:56.580 align:middle line:90%


01:04:56.580 --> 01:05:03.530 align:middle line:10%
Start to feel your neck, your
head, your arms, your legs,

01:05:03.530 --> 01:05:04.900 align:middle line:10%
your fingers, and your toes.

01:05:04.900 --> 01:05:11.080 align:middle line:90%


01:05:11.080 --> 01:05:17.040 align:middle line:10%
And whenever you're ready,
you can feel yourself back

01:05:17.040 --> 01:05:21.884 align:middle line:10%
into this room and
open your eyes.

01:05:21.884 --> 01:05:30.280 align:middle line:90%


01:05:30.280 --> 01:05:31.400 align:middle line:10%
Stretch.

01:05:31.400 --> 01:05:35.680 align:middle line:10%
And if you have water,
take a chug of your water.

01:05:35.680 --> 01:05:40.690 align:middle line:90%


01:05:40.690 --> 01:05:50.020 align:middle line:84%
Now, I said to you that
after I came back--

01:05:50.020 --> 01:05:53.350 align:middle line:84%
after I went home
from the hospital,

01:05:53.350 --> 01:05:57.250 align:middle line:84%
that's actually when
the real work began.

01:05:57.250 --> 01:05:59.500 align:middle line:84%
And I started
talking to my friends

01:05:59.500 --> 01:06:03.760 align:middle line:84%
about what I had experienced
on the other side.

01:06:03.760 --> 01:06:07.450 align:middle line:84%
I shared my story, much
like I shared with you--

01:06:07.450 --> 01:06:10.450 align:middle line:84%
that we are so much more
than physical beings,

01:06:10.450 --> 01:06:12.490 align:middle line:84%
that we are just the
tip of the iceberg,

01:06:12.490 --> 01:06:15.370 align:middle line:84%
that we're all connected,
and it was fear

01:06:15.370 --> 01:06:18.670 align:middle line:84%
that I felt that
was making me small

01:06:18.670 --> 01:06:23.290 align:middle line:84%
and suppressing my energy, which
is why the cancer had manifest.

01:06:23.290 --> 01:06:25.360 align:middle line:90%
And I was talking to them--

01:06:25.360 --> 01:06:27.290 align:middle line:84%
not just my friends,
but other people,

01:06:27.290 --> 01:06:29.450 align:middle line:84%
even people in the
medical community.

01:06:29.450 --> 01:06:31.600 align:middle line:84%
They wanted to understand
more what had happened,

01:06:31.600 --> 01:06:34.630 align:middle line:84%
because oncologists
said what had

01:06:34.630 --> 01:06:36.190 align:middle line:90%
happened to me was impossible.

01:06:36.190 --> 01:06:38.950 align:middle line:84%
But they had the medical
records to prove it.

01:06:38.950 --> 01:06:43.300 align:middle line:84%
And they said that
it was impossible

01:06:43.300 --> 01:06:47.420 align:middle line:84%
for billions of cancer cells
to leave my body so fast,

01:06:47.420 --> 01:06:49.990 align:middle line:84%
especially because
my body was so weak

01:06:49.990 --> 01:06:52.360 align:middle line:84%
and because my
organs had shut down.

01:06:52.360 --> 01:06:54.100 align:middle line:90%
And so they couldn't explain it.

01:06:54.100 --> 01:06:56.380 align:middle line:84%
So when I would explain
it in my own words,

01:06:56.380 --> 01:06:58.930 align:middle line:84%
they were like, no, no,
no, no, that stuff was just

01:06:58.930 --> 01:07:01.200 align:middle line:84%
your dying brain giving
you all these images.

01:07:01.200 --> 01:07:03.040 align:middle line:84%
We're trying to
understand the physical.

01:07:03.040 --> 01:07:05.020 align:middle line:90%
And I'm like, that is the point.

01:07:05.020 --> 01:07:09.100 align:middle line:84%
The physical is a reflection
of the non-physical.

01:07:09.100 --> 01:07:14.390 align:middle line:84%
But of course, people were
not quite with me on that.

01:07:14.390 --> 01:07:15.850 align:middle line:90%
So I was being challenged.

01:07:15.850 --> 01:07:18.730 align:middle line:84%
And even friends
of mine were like--

01:07:18.730 --> 01:07:20.920 align:middle line:84%
because I started
to say, oh, yeah,

01:07:20.920 --> 01:07:23.200 align:middle line:84%
you can't approach
illness with fear.

01:07:23.200 --> 01:07:24.760 align:middle line:90%
Their focus is on fear.

01:07:24.760 --> 01:07:26.590 align:middle line:90%
We got to love ourselves.

01:07:26.590 --> 01:07:30.550 align:middle line:90%
If you imagine that you were--

01:07:30.550 --> 01:07:33.380 align:middle line:84%
if you imagined that
you could see energy--

01:07:33.380 --> 01:07:35.590 align:middle line:84%
imagine if you could
see energy in your body.

01:07:35.590 --> 01:07:38.050 align:middle line:84%
When your energy
is at its highest

01:07:38.050 --> 01:07:41.200 align:middle line:84%
is when you love your life,
when you love yourself,

01:07:41.200 --> 01:07:43.510 align:middle line:84%
when you're passionate
about life, when you don't

01:07:43.510 --> 01:07:47.050 align:middle line:84%
have burdens on your shoulders,
when you're being who you are.

01:07:47.050 --> 01:07:50.200 align:middle line:84%
Now, that energy is
what keeps you healthy.

01:07:50.200 --> 01:07:54.140 align:middle line:84%
When you are in that energy
for prolonged periods of time,

01:07:54.140 --> 01:07:55.960 align:middle line:90%
you start to heal.

01:07:55.960 --> 01:07:58.360 align:middle line:84%
But when you are in
this energy of shrunken,

01:07:58.360 --> 01:08:03.730 align:middle line:84%
small, fear,
depression, hate myself,

01:08:03.730 --> 01:08:06.700 align:middle line:84%
pleasing people, doormat,
blah, blah, blah, blah--

01:08:06.700 --> 01:08:08.380 align:middle line:84%
then of course,
illnesses are going

01:08:08.380 --> 01:08:11.320 align:middle line:84%
to start to manifest,
because you're suppressing

01:08:11.320 --> 01:08:13.240 align:middle line:90%
your own life force energy.

01:08:13.240 --> 01:08:16.330 align:middle line:84%
So imagine if you
could see your energy.

01:08:16.330 --> 01:08:20.950 align:middle line:84%
And imagine if you could see
what activities increased

01:08:20.950 --> 01:08:24.290 align:middle line:84%
your energies and what
activities or what things you

01:08:24.290 --> 01:08:25.090 align:middle line:90%
say--

01:08:25.090 --> 01:08:27.910 align:middle line:84%
like, when I say "yes"
when I mean "no"--

01:08:27.910 --> 01:08:31.270 align:middle line:84%
imagine if you could immediately
see your energy diminish.

01:08:31.270 --> 01:08:33.250 align:middle line:84%
Now, if you could
see your energy,

01:08:33.250 --> 01:08:35.200 align:middle line:84%
you would make
different choices,

01:08:35.200 --> 01:08:37.840 align:middle line:84%
because you would have
this understanding

01:08:37.840 --> 01:08:42.279 align:middle line:84%
that if my energy is up and
out and big all the time,

01:08:42.279 --> 01:08:44.090 align:middle line:90%
there is no room for illness.

01:08:44.090 --> 01:08:47.479 align:middle line:84%
And so you would do things
that would feed your energy.

01:08:47.479 --> 01:08:49.670 align:middle line:84%
And when you do things
that feed your energy,

01:08:49.670 --> 01:08:51.850 align:middle line:84%
that's the energy you're
taking out into the world

01:08:51.850 --> 01:08:54.010 align:middle line:84%
and sharing with
everyone else, which

01:08:54.010 --> 01:08:58.120 align:middle line:84%
is why when you love yourself,
you're actually selfless,

01:08:58.120 --> 01:09:00.490 align:middle line:84%
because you're sharing that
love with everyone else.

01:09:00.490 --> 01:09:02.319 align:middle line:84%
When you don't love
yourself and you're

01:09:02.319 --> 01:09:04.750 align:middle line:84%
depressed and everything,
what are you doing?

01:09:04.750 --> 01:09:07.189 align:middle line:84%
You're drawing on
everyone else's energy.

01:09:07.189 --> 01:09:12.279 align:middle line:84%
So when we are taught that
it's selfish to love ourselves,

01:09:12.279 --> 01:09:15.490 align:middle line:84%
actually we're selfish when
we don't love ourselves,

01:09:15.490 --> 01:09:19.010 align:middle line:84%
because we're dependent on other
people's energies to feed us.

01:09:19.010 --> 01:09:20.319 align:middle line:90%
Does that make sense?

01:09:20.319 --> 01:09:23.800 align:middle line:84%
When you do love
yourself, you expand,

01:09:23.800 --> 01:09:26.600 align:middle line:84%
and you have energy,
which you bring with you.

01:09:26.600 --> 01:09:29.410 align:middle line:84%
So who would you rather sit
next to-- someone who loved

01:09:29.410 --> 01:09:31.540 align:middle line:84%
themselves or
someone who didn't?

01:09:31.540 --> 01:09:36.340 align:middle line:84%
So it's more selfish
not to love yourself.

01:09:36.340 --> 01:09:38.560 align:middle line:90%
So anyway, I was sharing this.

01:09:38.560 --> 01:09:41.289 align:middle line:84%
And people were telling
me, oh, you're delusional.

01:09:41.289 --> 01:09:42.729 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

01:09:42.729 --> 01:09:46.390 align:middle line:84%
I was like, yeah, but
it's what I learned.

01:09:46.390 --> 01:09:48.189 align:middle line:84%
But I thought people
would be interested.

01:09:48.189 --> 01:09:52.569 align:middle line:84%
And so they felt that,
no, you're not realistic.

01:09:52.569 --> 01:09:57.280 align:middle line:84%
You still have to go for the
conventional medical stuff.

01:09:57.280 --> 01:09:59.718 align:middle line:90%
And you still need all--

01:09:59.718 --> 01:10:00.760 align:middle line:90%
you've got to be careful.

01:10:00.760 --> 01:10:02.190 align:middle line:90%
You had cancer.

01:10:02.190 --> 01:10:03.250 align:middle line:90%
You better be careful.

01:10:03.250 --> 01:10:04.660 align:middle line:84%
You better go for
all your tests.

01:10:04.660 --> 01:10:05.460 align:middle line:90%
You better do this.

01:10:05.460 --> 01:10:06.830 align:middle line:90%
You better do that.

01:10:06.830 --> 01:10:10.060 align:middle line:84%
I wasn't going back into
that fear-based world,

01:10:10.060 --> 01:10:12.070 align:middle line:84%
because that is the
fear-based world where

01:10:12.070 --> 01:10:15.550 align:middle line:84%
you feel you've got to do this,
or the cancer will come back.

01:10:15.550 --> 01:10:18.170 align:middle line:84%
I tell people who've
had illnesses before,

01:10:18.170 --> 01:10:20.960 align:middle line:84%
I want you to focus on
your purpose for life.

01:10:20.960 --> 01:10:24.910 align:middle line:84%
I want you to focus on your
passion, your joy, your love,

01:10:24.910 --> 01:10:27.940 align:middle line:84%
who you love, loving
yourself, learning more about

01:10:27.940 --> 01:10:30.970 align:middle line:84%
who am I. That's what I had
to discover when I came back--

01:10:30.970 --> 01:10:32.320 align:middle line:90%
who am I, really?

01:10:32.320 --> 01:10:34.480 align:middle line:84%
Because I never
discovered that before.

01:10:34.480 --> 01:10:36.010 align:middle line:84%
Those are the
things you focus on.

01:10:36.010 --> 01:10:39.970 align:middle line:84%
Don't focus on, oh, I'm worried
I'm going to get cancer again,

01:10:39.970 --> 01:10:42.970 align:middle line:84%
because even when you think
you're doing everything

01:10:42.970 --> 01:10:48.850 align:middle line:84%
to prevent "cancer," all you're
doing is focusing on cancer.

01:10:48.850 --> 01:10:52.840 align:middle line:90%
It's not a real disease.

01:10:52.840 --> 01:10:54.580 align:middle line:90%
And I know that's provocative.

01:10:54.580 --> 01:10:56.405 align:middle line:90%
I've said that in public before.

01:10:56.405 --> 01:10:59.340 align:middle line:84%
And of course, people
will slander it.

01:10:59.340 --> 01:11:03.300 align:middle line:84%
But I will say it here,
that cancer is not

01:11:03.300 --> 01:11:04.380 align:middle line:90%
a physical disease.

01:11:04.380 --> 01:11:07.020 align:middle line:90%
It's a metaphysical disease.

01:11:07.020 --> 01:11:13.260 align:middle line:84%
But anyway, I realized that
I had to isolate myself

01:11:13.260 --> 01:11:16.890 align:middle line:90%
from that fear-based community.

01:11:16.890 --> 01:11:18.480 align:middle line:90%
And I did.

01:11:18.480 --> 01:11:20.640 align:middle line:84%
Thank god, my husband
who was with me

01:11:20.640 --> 01:11:22.320 align:middle line:90%
through the whole journey--

01:11:22.320 --> 01:11:24.310 align:middle line:90%
we both transformed together.

01:11:24.310 --> 01:11:27.720 align:middle line:84%
And so he knew he couldn't live
in that fear-based community,

01:11:27.720 --> 01:11:31.380 align:middle line:84%
either, because we had
experienced something which

01:11:31.380 --> 01:11:34.020 align:middle line:90%
even science didn't understand.

01:11:34.020 --> 01:11:36.060 align:middle line:90%
So we moved.

01:11:36.060 --> 01:11:38.910 align:middle line:84%
We moved to a neighborhood
where nobody knew us.

01:11:38.910 --> 01:11:41.640 align:middle line:84%
And it was only after, I
was able to really discover

01:11:41.640 --> 01:11:44.790 align:middle line:84%
who I am in a neighborhood
where I felt safe,

01:11:44.790 --> 01:11:46.230 align:middle line:90%
because nobody knew me.

01:11:46.230 --> 01:11:49.260 align:middle line:84%
There was no expectation
of who I used to be.

01:11:49.260 --> 01:11:52.800 align:middle line:84%
Now, when you don't allow
yourself to be who you are,

01:11:52.800 --> 01:11:55.470 align:middle line:84%
the message you are
sending yourself

01:11:55.470 --> 01:11:59.070 align:middle line:84%
is that I am not a
good person, so I

01:11:59.070 --> 01:12:02.940 align:middle line:84%
have to control who I am
and try to be someone else.

01:12:02.940 --> 01:12:07.020 align:middle line:84%
That's actually not true,
because who you are underneath

01:12:07.020 --> 01:12:10.830 align:middle line:90%
is consciousness, love, God.

01:12:10.830 --> 01:12:12.090 align:middle line:90%
That's who you are.

01:12:12.090 --> 01:12:14.640 align:middle line:90%
How dare you suppress that?

01:12:14.640 --> 01:12:17.910 align:middle line:84%
When you think about it,
how dare you suppress that?

01:12:17.910 --> 01:12:19.470 align:middle line:90%
That is your essence.

01:12:19.470 --> 01:12:21.990 align:middle line:84%
So when I started to
discover and started

01:12:21.990 --> 01:12:26.220 align:middle line:84%
to go inward and started
to discover who I am,

01:12:26.220 --> 01:12:28.890 align:middle line:90%
my life started to change.

01:12:28.890 --> 01:12:30.990 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to get out
and heal people.

01:12:30.990 --> 01:12:33.500 align:middle line:84%
But I was really
careful where I went.

01:12:33.500 --> 01:12:36.090 align:middle line:84%
And then I started
to discover that this

01:12:36.090 --> 01:12:38.160 align:middle line:90%
is what I wanted to do.

01:12:38.160 --> 01:12:41.940 align:middle line:84%
And I wrote about
it on a website.

01:12:41.940 --> 01:12:44.640 align:middle line:90%
I wrote about my NDE.

01:12:44.640 --> 01:12:47.850 align:middle line:84%
I signed it just
"Anita M's NDE--

01:12:47.850 --> 01:12:49.890 align:middle line:90%
Anita M's Near-Death Experience.

01:12:49.890 --> 01:12:53.490 align:middle line:84%
Unbeknownst to me, it
started to go viral.

01:12:53.490 --> 01:12:58.590 align:middle line:84%
And then it was discovered by
the late, great Dr. Wayne Dyer.

01:12:58.590 --> 01:13:00.570 align:middle line:84%
He discovered it
on the internet.

01:13:00.570 --> 01:13:02.850 align:middle line:84%
And he took it to
his publishers.

01:13:02.850 --> 01:13:04.980 align:middle line:90%
He told them, track her down.

01:13:04.980 --> 01:13:06.130 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

01:13:06.130 --> 01:13:07.030 align:middle line:90%
She agrees.

01:13:07.030 --> 01:13:08.010 align:middle line:90%
She agrees with me.

01:13:08.010 --> 01:13:10.800 align:middle line:90%
She's like, Wayne did that.

01:13:10.800 --> 01:13:12.640 align:middle line:90%
Wayne Dyer did that.

01:13:12.640 --> 01:13:13.440 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:13:13.440 --> 01:13:15.060 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

01:13:15.060 --> 01:13:15.900 align:middle line:90%
He's in the room.

01:13:15.900 --> 01:13:18.720 align:middle line:90%


01:13:18.720 --> 01:13:21.480 align:middle line:84%
The doggy can sense
Wayne in the room.

01:13:21.480 --> 01:13:27.900 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

01:13:27.900 --> 01:13:29.880 align:middle line:90%
Yep, he or she sees Wayne.

01:13:29.880 --> 01:13:31.020 align:middle line:90%
What a cute dog.

01:13:31.020 --> 01:13:32.850 align:middle line:90%
She's so cute.

01:13:32.850 --> 01:13:34.030 align:middle line:90%
Oh, that's me with the dog.

01:13:34.030 --> 01:13:36.340 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:13:36.340 --> 01:13:43.830 align:middle line:84%
So Wayne Dyer contacted me
and had Hay House contact me.

01:13:43.830 --> 01:13:46.320 align:middle line:90%
And they tracked me down.

01:13:46.320 --> 01:13:50.940 align:middle line:84%
And interestingly, I had
been reluctant to speak

01:13:50.940 --> 01:13:52.380 align:middle line:90%
about my story.

01:13:52.380 --> 01:13:57.720 align:middle line:84%
One day, a friend of mine
asked me to share my story

01:13:57.720 --> 01:13:59.130 align:middle line:90%
in a healing group.

01:13:59.130 --> 01:14:01.290 align:middle line:84%
And after I shared it
with the healing group

01:14:01.290 --> 01:14:04.690 align:middle line:84%
and I saw how they
were affected by it,

01:14:04.690 --> 01:14:06.970 align:middle line:90%
I realized that is my purpose.

01:14:06.970 --> 01:14:09.240 align:middle line:90%
My purpose is to share my story.

01:14:09.240 --> 01:14:13.590 align:middle line:84%
The very next day was the day
that I got an email from Hay

01:14:13.590 --> 01:14:16.650 align:middle line:84%
House, saying, Wayne Dyer
discovered your story

01:14:16.650 --> 01:14:20.700 align:middle line:84%
on the internet and has
asked us to track you down.

01:14:20.700 --> 01:14:23.740 align:middle line:84%
Now, I'd never communicated
with Hay House before.

01:14:23.740 --> 01:14:26.070 align:middle line:84%
I'd never communicated
with Wayne Dyer before.

01:14:26.070 --> 01:14:29.590 align:middle line:84%
It was the first I
was hearing of it.

01:14:29.590 --> 01:14:34.140 align:middle line:84%
And they said that
we want to ask you

01:14:34.140 --> 01:14:38.220 align:middle line:84%
if you would like to write
a book of your story, which

01:14:38.220 --> 01:14:43.650 align:middle line:84%
Wayne Dyer would like to
write the foreword to.

01:14:43.650 --> 01:14:45.930 align:middle line:90%
I was like, would I?

01:14:45.930 --> 01:14:49.050 align:middle line:84%
Who gets a book deal in an
email, just handed to them?

01:14:49.050 --> 01:14:50.550 align:middle line:84%
So they said, Wayne
Dyer would like

01:14:50.550 --> 01:14:51.720 align:middle line:90%
to write the foreword to it.

01:14:51.720 --> 01:14:56.940 align:middle line:84%
And he would like to share
it with his entire audience.

01:14:56.940 --> 01:14:58.390 align:middle line:90%
So I was like, whoa.

01:14:58.390 --> 01:15:02.190 align:middle line:84%
I started crying when
I got that email.

01:15:02.190 --> 01:15:04.260 align:middle line:90%
And so of course, I said, yes.

01:15:04.260 --> 01:15:06.300 align:middle line:84%
And I wrote back, and I
said, oh, my god, what

01:15:06.300 --> 01:15:07.100 align:middle line:90%
do I have to do?

01:15:07.100 --> 01:15:09.390 align:middle line:84%
So they said, we'll send
you a book contract,

01:15:09.390 --> 01:15:12.490 align:middle line:90%
and you just have to sign it.

01:15:12.490 --> 01:15:13.800 align:middle line:90%
I was living in Hong Kong.

01:15:13.800 --> 01:15:15.230 align:middle line:90%
I signed the contract.

01:15:15.230 --> 01:15:17.610 align:middle line:90%
Hay House flew me to the US.

01:15:17.610 --> 01:15:19.950 align:middle line:90%
I appeared on stage with Wayne.

01:15:19.950 --> 01:15:25.590 align:middle line:84%
He pulled me on stage in front
of an audience of 3,000 people.

01:15:25.590 --> 01:15:29.500 align:middle line:84%
And there was live streaming
for another two million.

01:15:29.500 --> 01:15:32.590 align:middle line:84%
And it was the first
time I was on stage.

01:15:32.590 --> 01:15:36.240 align:middle line:84%
And so I was sitting in
the audience, in the front.

01:15:36.240 --> 01:15:37.992 align:middle line:90%
And he starts to share my story.

01:15:37.992 --> 01:15:39.450 align:middle line:84%
And he says, and
there's this woman

01:15:39.450 --> 01:15:41.550 align:middle line:84%
in Hong Kong who died,
and then tells them

01:15:41.550 --> 01:15:43.470 align:middle line:90%
about cancer that healed.

01:15:43.470 --> 01:15:45.730 align:middle line:84%
And then he says,
but she's here,

01:15:45.730 --> 01:15:47.920 align:middle line:84%
so let me get her
to share it herself.

01:15:47.920 --> 01:15:49.290 align:middle line:90%
And I was shaking.

01:15:49.290 --> 01:15:51.690 align:middle line:90%
And he pulled me up on stage.

01:15:51.690 --> 01:15:52.830 align:middle line:90%
And he hands me the mic.

01:15:52.830 --> 01:15:55.470 align:middle line:84%
And he says, go on,
share your story.

01:15:55.470 --> 01:15:58.980 align:middle line:84%
So there I was in
front of 3,000 people.

01:15:58.980 --> 01:16:00.420 align:middle line:90%
And I was really shaking.

01:16:00.420 --> 01:16:03.600 align:middle line:90%
And he said, are you scared?

01:16:03.600 --> 01:16:04.980 align:middle line:90%
He was really incredulous.

01:16:04.980 --> 01:16:06.750 align:middle line:90%
He was like, are you scared?

01:16:06.750 --> 01:16:08.190 align:middle line:90%
And I said, of course I am.

01:16:08.190 --> 01:16:11.400 align:middle line:84%
I haven't spoken in front
of 3,000 people before.

01:16:11.400 --> 01:16:13.320 align:middle line:84%
He said, you've
been dead and back.

01:16:13.320 --> 01:16:16.780 align:middle line:84%
What have you got
to be scared about?

01:16:16.780 --> 01:16:19.380 align:middle line:84%
And I actually said
to him, it's easier

01:16:19.380 --> 01:16:21.270 align:middle line:90%
being dead than public speaking.

01:16:21.270 --> 01:16:24.140 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

01:16:24.140 --> 01:16:27.060 align:middle line:90%
And that's true.

01:16:27.060 --> 01:16:33.270 align:middle line:84%
But thanks to Wayne, my
book, "Dying to Be Me"--

01:16:33.270 --> 01:16:34.890 align:middle line:90%
he brought me on a TV show.

01:16:34.890 --> 01:16:37.380 align:middle line:90%
And it hit the New York Times.

01:16:37.380 --> 01:16:44.080 align:middle line:84%
And then it got published in 45
languages, which was amazing.

01:16:44.080 --> 01:16:46.350 align:middle line:84%
So the thing is,
what I discovered

01:16:46.350 --> 01:16:52.470 align:middle line:84%
later was that it took Hay House
five months to track me down,

01:16:52.470 --> 01:16:54.570 align:middle line:90%
because I was in Hong Kong.

01:16:54.570 --> 01:16:57.300 align:middle line:84%
I hadn't even put my
full name to the story,

01:16:57.300 --> 01:16:59.460 align:middle line:84%
because I wasn't sure
I wanted everyone

01:16:59.460 --> 01:17:01.360 align:middle line:90%
to know that it was me.

01:17:01.360 --> 01:17:07.140 align:middle line:84%
But having said that, the
day that they found me

01:17:07.140 --> 01:17:11.130 align:middle line:84%
was the day that I knew
that my purpose was

01:17:11.130 --> 01:17:13.510 align:middle line:90%
to share my story, to the day.

01:17:13.510 --> 01:17:16.710 align:middle line:84%
It was like, the night I
realized, this is my purpose,

01:17:16.710 --> 01:17:18.360 align:middle line:84%
this is what I'm
meant to be doing--

01:17:18.360 --> 01:17:21.780 align:middle line:84%
the next morning, the
email landed in my mailbox.

01:17:21.780 --> 01:17:26.550 align:middle line:84%
So my point is, I said
we are all connected.

01:17:26.550 --> 01:17:30.330 align:middle line:84%
When you are ready for
something, it comes to you.

01:17:30.330 --> 01:17:32.760 align:middle line:84%
You don't need to
go out and chase it.

01:17:32.760 --> 01:17:34.200 align:middle line:90%
It comes to you.

01:17:34.200 --> 01:17:36.360 align:middle line:84%
You just have to
be ready for it.

01:17:36.360 --> 01:17:41.580 align:middle line:84%
Now, as the years have gone
on and I'm living this life

01:17:41.580 --> 01:17:44.970 align:middle line:84%
post-NDE, where I feel
I have created my life--

01:17:44.970 --> 01:17:47.580 align:middle line:90%
pre-NDE, I was reacting to life.

01:17:47.580 --> 01:17:50.760 align:middle line:90%
Post-NDE, I'm creating my life.

01:17:50.760 --> 01:17:53.520 align:middle line:84%
Those same old friends
that said I was delusional,

01:17:53.520 --> 01:17:54.560 align:middle line:90%
they're back in my life.

01:17:54.560 --> 01:17:56.550 align:middle line:84%
They're like, oh, my
god, I love your life.

01:17:56.550 --> 01:17:57.930 align:middle line:90%
I want what you have.

01:17:57.930 --> 01:17:59.730 align:middle line:90%
How do I do what you do?

01:17:59.730 --> 01:18:02.050 align:middle line:84%
And I said, I guess you
got to be delusional.

01:18:02.050 --> 01:18:03.890 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

01:18:03.890 --> 01:18:07.110 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

01:18:07.110 --> 01:18:08.550 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:18:08.550 --> 01:18:11.520 align:middle line:90%
So stay on your unicorn.

01:18:11.520 --> 01:18:14.310 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

01:18:14.310 --> 01:18:16.470 align:middle line:90%
And just follow your dreams.

01:18:16.470 --> 01:18:17.820 align:middle line:90%
And don't chase them.

01:18:17.820 --> 01:18:21.348 align:middle line:84%
Every time you feel you have
to chase and pursue and fight,

01:18:21.348 --> 01:18:22.890 align:middle line:84%
you're just telling
yourself-- you're

01:18:22.890 --> 01:18:26.820 align:middle line:84%
sending the message that I'm
not good enough for this.

01:18:26.820 --> 01:18:29.640 align:middle line:84%
You need to feel it
from the inside--

01:18:29.640 --> 01:18:34.020 align:middle line:84%
from the inside-out,
from the inside-out.

01:18:34.020 --> 01:18:38.760 align:middle line:84%
Illness, as well-- the physical
is the last place anything

01:18:38.760 --> 01:18:39.930 align:middle line:90%
shows up.

01:18:39.930 --> 01:18:41.880 align:middle line:90%
It starts from the inside.

01:18:41.880 --> 01:18:44.262 align:middle line:84%
Now, I want to go into
a couple of questions.

01:18:44.262 --> 01:18:45.970 align:middle line:84%
I know a couple of
people have questions.

01:18:45.970 --> 01:18:50.400 align:middle line:10%
But before I do, I created
a near-death experience

01:18:50.400 --> 01:18:51.930 align:middle line:10%
meditation CD.

01:18:51.930 --> 01:18:55.980 align:middle line:84%
And I just want to give them out
to two people, any two people.

01:18:55.980 --> 01:18:58.830 align:middle line:84%
And I'm just going to
throw one on each side.

01:18:58.830 --> 01:19:01.060 align:middle line:90%
I wish I had 500.

01:19:01.060 --> 01:19:02.380 align:middle line:90%
Oop.

01:19:02.380 --> 01:19:03.420 align:middle line:90%
Oops.

01:19:03.420 --> 01:19:05.400 align:middle line:84%
See, and I was
throwing it that way.

01:19:05.400 --> 01:19:06.900 align:middle line:90%
See, you were meant to get it.

01:19:06.900 --> 01:19:09.050 align:middle line:90%
One on this side.

01:19:09.050 --> 01:19:10.930 align:middle line:10%
Oops.

01:19:10.930 --> 01:19:12.810 align:middle line:90%
I am so sorry.

01:19:12.810 --> 01:19:14.550 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:19:14.550 --> 01:19:17.820 align:middle line:84%
So that meditation
CD, I'm so thrilled.

01:19:17.820 --> 01:19:21.220 align:middle line:84%
We put it out on 2nd of
February, like, a week ago,

01:19:21.220 --> 01:19:22.190 align:middle line:90%
which is--

01:19:22.190 --> 01:19:24.360 align:middle line:84%
no, two weeks, three
weeks ago, because that

01:19:24.360 --> 01:19:27.730 align:middle line:90%
is the anniversary of my NDE.

01:19:27.730 --> 01:19:29.490 align:middle line:90%
And it hit the billboard charts.

01:19:29.490 --> 01:19:30.360 align:middle line:90%
It hit number 2.

01:19:30.360 --> 01:19:31.330 align:middle line:90%
We were so happy.

01:19:31.330 --> 01:19:34.620 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

01:19:34.620 --> 01:19:35.640 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:19:35.640 --> 01:19:37.560 align:middle line:10%
For anyone who's
interested, also, I

01:19:37.560 --> 01:19:40.050 align:middle line:10%
do a lot of retreats
and events where

01:19:40.050 --> 01:19:43.260 align:middle line:10%
we like to take people
into that space of feeling

01:19:43.260 --> 01:19:44.910 align:middle line:10%
like they are expanded.

01:19:44.910 --> 01:19:48.030 align:middle line:10%
And we keep you in that space
for the entire duration.

01:19:48.030 --> 01:19:50.290 align:middle line:10%
I'm doing a cruise in June--

01:19:50.290 --> 01:19:53.850 align:middle line:10%
an Alaska cruise, where we
get to see real icebergs.

01:19:53.850 --> 01:19:55.890 align:middle line:84%
So if anyone wants
to join me, we've

01:19:55.890 --> 01:19:58.350 align:middle line:84%
left a flyer on
the chair for you.

01:19:58.350 --> 01:20:00.810 align:middle line:84%
So I would love it if
you guys joined me.

01:20:00.810 --> 01:20:03.990 align:middle line:10%
It's seven days of
lectures and fun

01:20:03.990 --> 01:20:06.010 align:middle line:10%
and tours and stuff like that.

01:20:06.010 --> 01:20:10.710 align:middle line:84%
So I think I have time
for, like, two questions.

01:20:10.710 --> 01:20:11.940 align:middle line:90%
Anybody?

01:20:11.940 --> 01:20:13.620 align:middle line:84%
You had a question
from the beginning,

01:20:13.620 --> 01:20:15.730 align:middle line:90%
so I'll let you go first.

01:20:15.730 --> 01:20:17.500 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, [INAUDIBLE].

01:20:17.500 --> 01:20:19.930 align:middle line:84%
>> Yes, wait for-- yeah,
there's a microphone there.

01:20:19.930 --> 01:20:21.760 align:middle line:84%
Yes, if you have a
question, there's

01:20:21.760 --> 01:20:23.930 align:middle line:90%
a microphone right there.

01:20:23.930 --> 01:20:24.730 align:middle line:90%
I didn't realize.

01:20:24.730 --> 01:20:26.200 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:20:26.200 --> 01:20:27.490 align:middle line:90%
Yes, please.

01:20:27.490 --> 01:20:29.890 align:middle line:90%
Thanks.

01:20:29.890 --> 01:20:31.200 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

01:20:31.200 --> 01:20:37.950 align:middle line:84%
Well, I also had a
afterlife experience.

01:20:37.950 --> 01:20:41.660 align:middle line:84%
And I was just
curious what you seen?

01:20:41.660 --> 01:20:45.480 align:middle line:84%
Because I seen a amber
energy, amber light.

01:20:45.480 --> 01:20:49.240 align:middle line:84%
Our bodies were reddish orange,
and everything else was yellow.

01:20:49.240 --> 01:20:50.250 align:middle line:90%
And I saw my friends.

01:20:50.250 --> 01:20:53.130 align:middle line:84%
And I still saw the
shape of their body,

01:20:53.130 --> 01:20:57.210 align:middle line:90%
but I didn't actually see--

01:20:57.210 --> 01:21:00.730 align:middle line:84%
I didn't see any form, their
facial features, or anything

01:21:00.730 --> 01:21:01.530 align:middle line:90%
like that.

01:21:01.530 --> 01:21:02.640 align:middle line:90%
>> That's exactly it.

01:21:02.640 --> 01:21:05.560 align:middle line:84%
You don't see their
facial features.

01:21:05.560 --> 01:21:06.870 align:middle line:90%
But you kind of see their form.

01:21:06.870 --> 01:21:09.720 align:middle line:84%
And you know from their
essence that it's them.

01:21:09.720 --> 01:21:12.720 align:middle line:84%
And also, there was
a lot of clarity.

01:21:12.720 --> 01:21:14.820 align:middle line:84%
So in terms of what I
could see, the colors

01:21:14.820 --> 01:21:17.130 align:middle line:90%
were clearer than here.

01:21:17.130 --> 01:21:20.700 align:middle line:84%
But it was like wherever
I put my awareness, that's

01:21:20.700 --> 01:21:21.900 align:middle line:90%
where I was.

01:21:21.900 --> 01:21:24.000 align:middle line:90%
A metaphor that I often use--

01:21:24.000 --> 01:21:27.030 align:middle line:84%
it was like I could see
everything all at once.

01:21:27.030 --> 01:21:30.900 align:middle line:84%
And if you watch my TED
Talk, you'll see this.

01:21:30.900 --> 01:21:33.030 align:middle line:90%
And I've even got it in my book.

01:21:33.030 --> 01:21:35.340 align:middle line:84%
A metaphor I use
is the warehouse.

01:21:35.340 --> 01:21:38.280 align:middle line:84%
It's as if you've
spent your whole life

01:21:38.280 --> 01:21:41.940 align:middle line:84%
in a darkened warehouse
with one little flashlight.

01:21:41.940 --> 01:21:45.720 align:middle line:84%
And everything
you've ever seen is

01:21:45.720 --> 01:21:48.720 align:middle line:84%
just what your little
flashlight has shone on.

01:21:48.720 --> 01:21:51.670 align:middle line:84%
So you can only see
one thing at a time.

01:21:51.670 --> 01:21:53.490 align:middle line:90%
One day, the flood lights go on.

01:21:53.490 --> 01:21:57.840 align:middle line:84%
And you realize that you're in
this huge warehouse with lots

01:21:57.840 --> 01:22:00.660 align:middle line:84%
and lots of things-- many
things you've never seen before,

01:22:00.660 --> 01:22:03.120 align:middle line:84%
because your flashlight
never shone on it.

01:22:03.120 --> 01:22:05.610 align:middle line:84%
And that's what it
felt like in my NDE.

01:22:05.610 --> 01:22:07.770 align:middle line:84%
It was like I was
aware that everything

01:22:07.770 --> 01:22:09.880 align:middle line:90%
existed simultaneously.

01:22:09.880 --> 01:22:13.050 align:middle line:84%
In fact, I was aware, from
that perspective, looking down

01:22:13.050 --> 01:22:17.040 align:middle line:84%
on physical life,
that on this life--

01:22:17.040 --> 01:22:20.130 align:middle line:84%
the bad, the good, the negative,
the positive-- everything

01:22:20.130 --> 01:22:21.810 align:middle line:90%
exists simultaneously.

01:22:21.810 --> 01:22:25.410 align:middle line:84%
But what we experience is
what we shine our light on.

01:22:25.410 --> 01:22:29.190 align:middle line:84%
So for example, dark and
light-- fear and love.

01:22:29.190 --> 01:22:31.770 align:middle line:84%
All of this exists
simultaneously.

01:22:31.770 --> 01:22:35.040 align:middle line:84%
But it depends what
we shine our light on.

01:22:35.040 --> 01:22:39.960 align:middle line:84%
And people seem to believe that
where their light is focused--

01:22:39.960 --> 01:22:42.990 align:middle line:84%
when the warehouse is dark
and you can't see anything

01:22:42.990 --> 01:22:45.360 align:middle line:84%
except what your
flashlight is shining on,

01:22:45.360 --> 01:22:47.700 align:middle line:84%
you think that's all
there is to life.

01:22:47.700 --> 01:22:50.360 align:middle line:84%
So if your light
is shining on fear,

01:22:50.360 --> 01:22:52.530 align:middle line:84%
you think, wow, life
is fearful, when

01:22:52.530 --> 01:22:58.380 align:middle line:84%
you don't realize that love and
joy and passion also all exist.

01:22:58.380 --> 01:23:00.810 align:middle line:84%
So what I always tell
people, the flashlight

01:23:00.810 --> 01:23:04.980 align:middle line:84%
is the analogy of our
awareness while we're here.

01:23:04.980 --> 01:23:07.110 align:middle line:84%
And when you're there,
you become aware

01:23:07.110 --> 01:23:08.220 align:middle line:90%
of the whole thing.

01:23:08.220 --> 01:23:12.610 align:middle line:84%
And over here, our awareness is
only focused on a little piece.

01:23:12.610 --> 01:23:14.820 align:middle line:84%
And just real quickly,
I want to try something

01:23:14.820 --> 01:23:16.740 align:middle line:90%
that I did before.

01:23:16.740 --> 01:23:19.830 align:middle line:84%
For those of you who've not
watched my TED Talk or heard me

01:23:19.830 --> 01:23:24.660 align:middle line:84%
speak before, I want you to
look around the room and find

01:23:24.660 --> 01:23:29.820 align:middle line:84%
everything in the room
that is red in color--

01:23:29.820 --> 01:23:32.790 align:middle line:84%
any family of red,
red-orange, dark red--

01:23:32.790 --> 01:23:34.470 align:middle line:90%
and commit it to your memory.

01:23:34.470 --> 01:23:36.900 align:middle line:84%
Anything in the room--
look around, look around.

01:23:36.900 --> 01:23:38.830 align:middle line:90%
Commit it to your memory.

01:23:38.830 --> 01:23:39.630 align:middle line:90%
OK.

01:23:39.630 --> 01:23:41.620 align:middle line:84%
And I'm going to
test you in a minute.

01:23:41.620 --> 01:23:43.320 align:middle line:90%
So face the front.

01:23:43.320 --> 01:23:44.730 align:middle line:90%
Now face the front.

01:23:44.730 --> 01:23:46.320 align:middle line:90%
Close your eyes.

01:23:46.320 --> 01:23:47.730 align:middle line:90%
No peeking.

01:23:47.730 --> 01:23:50.370 align:middle line:84%
Now I want you to
recollect everything

01:23:50.370 --> 01:23:52.552 align:middle line:90%
in the room that's blue.

01:23:52.552 --> 01:23:56.710 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

01:23:56.710 --> 01:23:58.400 align:middle line:90%
Anything?

01:23:58.400 --> 01:23:59.200 align:middle line:90%
OK.

01:23:59.200 --> 01:24:03.760 align:middle line:84%
So now open your
eyes, and look around.

01:24:03.760 --> 01:24:06.250 align:middle line:90%
Look around at what you missed.

01:24:06.250 --> 01:24:08.170 align:middle line:84%
You're probably wearing
something yourself

01:24:08.170 --> 01:24:11.440 align:middle line:84%
that you forgot that's
blue-- your own shirt.

01:24:11.440 --> 01:24:13.450 align:middle line:84%
And here's the thing--
from where I'm standing,

01:24:13.450 --> 01:24:15.940 align:middle line:84%
there's more blue in
the room than red.

01:24:15.940 --> 01:24:18.700 align:middle line:84%
Your flashlight
was focused on red.

01:24:18.700 --> 01:24:20.950 align:middle line:84%
But there's more blue
in the room than red.

01:24:20.950 --> 01:24:22.760 align:middle line:90%
That's what we do with fear.

01:24:22.760 --> 01:24:23.890 align:middle line:90%
Fear sells.

01:24:23.890 --> 01:24:27.040 align:middle line:84%
So people will keep
feeding you fear.

01:24:27.040 --> 01:24:29.000 align:middle line:84%
As long as you keep
your awareness--

01:24:29.000 --> 01:24:31.060 align:middle line:84%
your flashlight--
focused on fear,

01:24:31.060 --> 01:24:33.250 align:middle line:84%
that will be your
experience of the world.

01:24:33.250 --> 01:24:36.670 align:middle line:84%
And you will completely
miss the joy, passion, love,

01:24:36.670 --> 01:24:39.332 align:middle line:84%
of which there is
more of in the world.

01:24:39.332 --> 01:24:41.040 align:middle line:84%
So that was the reason
for that exercise.

01:24:41.040 --> 01:24:41.984 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

01:24:41.984 --> 01:24:42.928 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:24:42.928 --> 01:24:45.290 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:24:45.290 --> 01:24:49.690 align:middle line:90%
And let's do one more question.

01:24:49.690 --> 01:24:51.040 align:middle line:90%
Yes, come on up to the mic.

01:24:51.040 --> 01:24:52.000 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:24:52.000 --> 01:24:54.880 align:middle line:90%


01:24:54.880 --> 01:24:59.200 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

01:24:59.200 --> 01:25:01.600 align:middle line:84%
>> They call me Mr.
Red, by the way.

01:25:01.600 --> 01:25:02.682 align:middle line:90%
>> I love it.

01:25:02.682 --> 01:25:03.890 align:middle line:90%
>> I have a question for you.

01:25:03.890 --> 01:25:05.682 align:middle line:84%
I've heard the thing
about loving yourself.

01:25:05.682 --> 01:25:07.720 align:middle line:84%
And I never got the
proper definition.

01:25:07.720 --> 01:25:10.300 align:middle line:84%
Can you explain,
how do you love--

01:25:10.300 --> 01:25:11.580 align:middle line:90%
how do you love yourself?

01:25:11.580 --> 01:25:13.840 align:middle line:84%
Do you buy a lot
of expensive things

01:25:13.840 --> 01:25:15.380 align:middle line:90%
or buy things for people?

01:25:15.380 --> 01:25:16.990 align:middle line:90%
That's what I wanted to ask you.

01:25:16.990 --> 01:25:18.590 align:middle line:90%
I've heard about, love yourself.

01:25:18.590 --> 01:25:20.840 align:middle line:84%
But I've never found
out, how do you do it?

01:25:20.840 --> 01:25:21.640 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:25:21.640 --> 01:25:22.510 align:middle line:90%
>> Great question.

01:25:22.510 --> 01:25:23.530 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:25:23.530 --> 01:25:24.580 align:middle line:90%
Thank you, Mr. Red.

01:25:24.580 --> 01:25:27.140 align:middle line:90%


01:25:27.140 --> 01:25:28.280 align:middle line:90%
So there's many ways.

01:25:28.280 --> 01:25:31.510 align:middle line:84%
So first of all, it's
to love your whole self.

01:25:31.510 --> 01:25:33.290 align:middle line:84%
I like buying
expensive things, too.

01:25:33.290 --> 01:25:35.275 align:middle line:84%
But I like it when
people give me--

01:25:35.275 --> 01:25:36.900 align:middle line:84%
but anyway, that's
a whole other thing.

01:25:36.900 --> 01:25:38.140 align:middle line:90%
No.

01:25:38.140 --> 01:25:39.860 align:middle line:90%
So loving yourself does not--

01:25:39.860 --> 01:25:40.660 align:middle line:90%
I'm kidding.

01:25:40.660 --> 01:25:44.090 align:middle line:84%
Loving yourself does not
mean buying expensive things.

01:25:44.090 --> 01:25:44.890 align:middle line:90%
But you can.

01:25:44.890 --> 01:25:46.690 align:middle line:90%
It's OK.

01:25:46.690 --> 01:25:49.480 align:middle line:84%
When you don't love
yourself, you actually

01:25:49.480 --> 01:25:52.630 align:middle line:84%
do things to
compensate, like buying

01:25:52.630 --> 01:25:54.850 align:middle line:84%
yourself expensive
things, trying to keep up

01:25:54.850 --> 01:25:56.080 align:middle line:90%
with fashion, and all.

01:25:56.080 --> 01:25:58.300 align:middle line:84%
When you love
yourself, you actually

01:25:58.300 --> 01:26:00.190 align:middle line:90%
lose interest in those things.

01:26:00.190 --> 01:26:02.380 align:middle line:84%
That's what I
actually want to say.

01:26:02.380 --> 01:26:06.340 align:middle line:84%
Now, when you love yourself,
you're unafraid to say no.

01:26:06.340 --> 01:26:07.900 align:middle line:90%
You're unafraid to say no.

01:26:07.900 --> 01:26:11.860 align:middle line:84%
You're unafraid
to honor yourself.

01:26:11.860 --> 01:26:13.360 align:middle line:90%
You put your health first--

01:26:13.360 --> 01:26:15.430 align:middle line:84%
your well-being,
sorry, not health--

01:26:15.430 --> 01:26:17.830 align:middle line:84%
your well-being
before anything else.

01:26:17.830 --> 01:26:19.990 align:middle line:84%
When you don't
love yourself, you

01:26:19.990 --> 01:26:22.690 align:middle line:90%
fear not having enough money.

01:26:22.690 --> 01:26:25.690 align:middle line:84%
You say yes to things
for the sake of money,

01:26:25.690 --> 01:26:28.450 align:middle line:84%
as opposed to for the
sake of well-being.

01:26:28.450 --> 01:26:31.300 align:middle line:84%
So for example, if
you're in a job you hate,

01:26:31.300 --> 01:26:33.400 align:middle line:84%
it means you don't
love yourself enough.

01:26:33.400 --> 01:26:35.870 align:middle line:84%
If you're in an
abusive relationship

01:26:35.870 --> 01:26:37.570 align:middle line:84%
but you're too
afraid to get out,

01:26:37.570 --> 01:26:39.640 align:middle line:84%
it means you don't
love yourself enough.

01:26:39.640 --> 01:26:42.700 align:middle line:84%
You're not giving yourself
the same priority that you're

01:26:42.700 --> 01:26:44.080 align:middle line:90%
giving other people.

01:26:44.080 --> 01:26:46.210 align:middle line:84%
If you fall flat on
your face and fail

01:26:46.210 --> 01:26:48.190 align:middle line:84%
and you judge yourself
and beat yourself

01:26:48.190 --> 01:26:50.380 align:middle line:84%
up more than anyone
else does, that

01:26:50.380 --> 01:26:52.360 align:middle line:84%
means you don't love
yourself enough.

01:26:52.360 --> 01:26:54.520 align:middle line:84%
So those are examples
of not loving yourself.

01:26:54.520 --> 01:26:56.200 align:middle line:84%
When you love
yourself, you realize

01:26:56.200 --> 01:26:58.960 align:middle line:84%
you are much more than
your physical being.

01:26:58.960 --> 01:27:01.730 align:middle line:84%
You realize you have
a greater purpose.

01:27:01.730 --> 01:27:06.220 align:middle line:84%
And you put your
well-being-- your health--

01:27:06.220 --> 01:27:09.690 align:middle line:84%
you realize you are an
expression of the divine,

01:27:09.690 --> 01:27:11.080 align:middle line:90%
of consciousness.

01:27:11.080 --> 01:27:13.690 align:middle line:90%
And that is a priority to you--

01:27:13.690 --> 01:27:17.800 align:middle line:84%
to be that channel, to be
that vessel for the divine

01:27:17.800 --> 01:27:20.420 align:middle line:90%
to express itself through you.

01:27:20.420 --> 01:27:24.700 align:middle line:84%
And in order for the divine
to express itself through you,

01:27:24.700 --> 01:27:27.890 align:middle line:84%
you do whatever it takes
to be that channel.

01:27:27.890 --> 01:27:31.330 align:middle line:84%
And if it means sometimes
spending more money on things,

01:27:31.330 --> 01:27:35.680 align:middle line:84%
or if it means sitting in first
class for your well-being,

01:27:35.680 --> 01:27:37.420 align:middle line:84%
you do that, because
your well-being

01:27:37.420 --> 01:27:38.930 align:middle line:90%
is the most important thing.

01:27:38.930 --> 01:27:41.710 align:middle line:84%
But you do it for different
reasons than someone

01:27:41.710 --> 01:27:45.930 align:middle line:84%
who is just trying to compensate
for not loving themselves.

01:27:45.930 --> 01:27:49.990 align:middle line:84%
And for me, the big one
that I learned was I

01:27:49.990 --> 01:27:54.340 align:middle line:84%
realized that I was doing
things for the wrong reasons.

01:27:54.340 --> 01:27:58.450 align:middle line:84%
I was doing things because I was
afraid of disappointing people.

01:27:58.450 --> 01:27:59.920 align:middle line:90%
That was the big one for me.

01:27:59.920 --> 01:28:02.230 align:middle line:84%
So for me, the big one
about loving myself

01:28:02.230 --> 01:28:04.510 align:middle line:90%
was learning to say no.

01:28:04.510 --> 01:28:07.150 align:middle line:84%
So I hope that
clarified somewhat.

01:28:07.150 --> 01:28:10.165 align:middle line:90%
Let's do one last one, I think.

01:28:10.165 --> 01:28:13.150 align:middle line:84%
>> I was just curious
about one thing--

01:28:13.150 --> 01:28:14.290 align:middle line:90%
>> They can't hear you.

01:28:14.290 --> 01:28:15.620 align:middle line:90%
They can't hear you.

01:28:15.620 --> 01:28:17.060 align:middle line:84%
>> It was just a
snippet to what--

01:28:17.060 --> 01:28:17.660 align:middle line:90%
>> That's all right.

01:28:17.660 --> 01:28:18.493 align:middle line:90%
We want to hear you.

01:28:18.493 --> 01:28:21.480 align:middle line:84%
>> Do you think it's possible
that it's a practice?

01:28:21.480 --> 01:28:23.270 align:middle line:84%
It's not just getting
in that right place

01:28:23.270 --> 01:28:25.020 align:middle line:84%
or buying the first
class, but it's really

01:28:25.020 --> 01:28:29.510 align:middle line:84%
maybe a practice that's a daily
sort of practice to love self

01:28:29.510 --> 01:28:31.730 align:middle line:84%
to get into that
place more often?

01:28:31.730 --> 01:28:33.050 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

01:28:33.050 --> 01:28:34.360 align:middle line:90%
It is a practice.

01:28:34.360 --> 01:28:37.640 align:middle line:84%
So first, there has
to be that insight.

01:28:37.640 --> 01:28:41.720 align:middle line:84%
There has to be the
insight, the desire.

01:28:41.720 --> 01:28:43.550 align:middle line:90%
That has to come first.

01:28:43.550 --> 01:28:45.980 align:middle line:90%
But it does take time.

01:28:45.980 --> 01:28:47.600 align:middle line:90%
And you know why it takes time?

01:28:47.600 --> 01:28:49.280 align:middle line:90%
Because we've built a habit.

01:28:49.280 --> 01:28:53.150 align:middle line:84%
We've made a habit of
putting ourselves last.

01:28:53.150 --> 01:28:56.210 align:middle line:84%
And so we have to kind
of undo that habit.

01:28:56.210 --> 01:28:57.560 align:middle line:90%
We have to become aware.

01:28:57.560 --> 01:28:59.780 align:middle line:84%
Whenever you're
putting yourself last,

01:28:59.780 --> 01:29:03.090 align:middle line:84%
you have to become aware
that, oh, I'm doing it again,

01:29:03.090 --> 01:29:04.950 align:middle line:90%
I'm putting myself last again.

01:29:04.950 --> 01:29:07.310 align:middle line:84%
We really have to
become aware of that.

01:29:07.310 --> 01:29:08.720 align:middle line:84%
How many people
here have trouble

01:29:08.720 --> 01:29:12.840 align:middle line:84%
saying no when you really
don't want to do something?

01:29:12.840 --> 01:29:13.640 align:middle line:90%
OK.

01:29:13.640 --> 01:29:17.630 align:middle line:84%
So here's something I
want you to remember.

01:29:17.630 --> 01:29:19.790 align:middle line:84%
When you say yes
because you're just

01:29:19.790 --> 01:29:22.700 align:middle line:84%
afraid of disappointing
someone, now

01:29:22.700 --> 01:29:24.620 align:middle line:90%
imagine-- just imagine this.

01:29:24.620 --> 01:29:29.720 align:middle line:84%
Imagine if everything that
everyone has ever done for you,

01:29:29.720 --> 01:29:32.720 align:middle line:84%
they've done it because they're
afraid if they don't do it,

01:29:32.720 --> 01:29:34.510 align:middle line:90%
they'll disappoint you.

01:29:34.510 --> 01:29:35.310 align:middle line:90%
Imagine.

01:29:35.310 --> 01:29:36.750 align:middle line:90%
How does that feel?

01:29:36.750 --> 01:29:38.990 align:middle line:84%
How does that feel
if people have--

01:29:38.990 --> 01:29:41.780 align:middle line:84%
everyone that's said
yes to you, have said it

01:29:41.780 --> 01:29:44.540 align:middle line:84%
because they're
afraid of saying no,

01:29:44.540 --> 01:29:47.730 align:middle line:84%
not because they really
want to do it for you,

01:29:47.730 --> 01:29:50.210 align:middle line:84%
but because they're
afraid of saying no.

01:29:50.210 --> 01:29:54.020 align:middle line:84%
Don't you wish that they
would rather have been honest?

01:29:54.020 --> 01:29:55.400 align:middle line:90%
You do, right?

01:29:55.400 --> 01:29:57.710 align:middle line:90%
That's where the dissonance is.

01:29:57.710 --> 01:30:00.860 align:middle line:84%
We don't like the feeling
of someone doing it to us.

01:30:00.860 --> 01:30:02.970 align:middle line:84%
But we do it to other
people and think

01:30:02.970 --> 01:30:04.910 align:middle line:90%
we're good people for doing it.

01:30:04.910 --> 01:30:08.210 align:middle line:84%
We think that, oh, I'm
too nice to say no.

01:30:08.210 --> 01:30:09.950 align:middle line:90%
That's a dissonance.

01:30:09.950 --> 01:30:14.180 align:middle line:84%
That's the dissonance that
gets you to become inauthentic.

01:30:14.180 --> 01:30:15.020 align:middle line:90%
That's the trap.

01:30:15.020 --> 01:30:16.040 align:middle line:90%
So remember that.

01:30:16.040 --> 01:30:17.000 align:middle line:90%
Remember that.

01:30:17.000 --> 01:30:19.970 align:middle line:84%
Treat other people the way
you want to be treated.

01:30:19.970 --> 01:30:23.480 align:middle line:84%
But don't forget,
love yourself first.

01:30:23.480 --> 01:30:27.385 align:middle line:84%
And so if you want other
people to be honest with you

01:30:27.385 --> 01:30:28.760 align:middle line:84%
and say no to you
when they don't

01:30:28.760 --> 01:30:32.130 align:middle line:84%
feel like doing something,
do that for them, as well.

01:30:32.130 --> 01:30:35.030 align:middle line:84%
So thank you all for
coming this morning.

01:30:35.030 --> 01:30:37.370 align:middle line:90%
I so appreciate you.

